blocks.name: unierri
blocks.content: If we approximate a chain of unitary transformations (quantum computer gates) ` F ` , ` G ` by other unitary transformations ` S ` , ` T ` , the error increases at most additively. Equation 4.73 of [NielsenChuang] p. 195. (Contributed by NM, 10-Mar-2006.) (New usage is discouraged.)

thm unierri(class c0, class c1, class c2, class c3) {
  ⊢ (normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))[≤]((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[+](normop `(c1[-op]c3)))
  ⊣ c0 ∈ UniOp
  ⊣ c1 ∈ UniOp
  ⊣ c2 ∈ UniOp
  ⊣ c3 ∈ UniOp
} = {
  pm2.61ine(chba, c0h, (normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))[≤]((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[+](normop `(c1[-op]c3))))
  eqbrtrd((normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))), cle, ((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[+](normop `(c1[-op]c3))), nat0, ~H = 0H)
  mpan2(~H = 0H, (normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))= 0, (((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)): ~H → ~H))
  hosubcli((c0 ∘ c1), (c2 ∘ c3))
  nmop0h(((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))
  syl5breqr(nat0, cle, ((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[+](normop `(c1[-op]c3))), (0[+]0), ~H = 0H)
  breqtrri(nat0, cle, (0[+]0), nat0)
  0le0()
  00id()
  oveq12d((normop `(c0[-op]c2)), caddc, (normop `(c1[-op]c3)), nat0, nat0, ~H = 0H)
  mpan2(~H = 0H, (normop `(c0[-op]c2))= 0, ((c0[-op]c2): ~H → ~H))
  hosubcli(c0, c2)
  nmop0h((c0[-op]c2))
  mpan2(~H = 0H, (normop `(c1[-op]c3))= 0, ((c1[-op]c3): ~H → ~H))
  hosubcli(c1, c3)
  nmop0h((c1[-op]c3))
  syl5breq((normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))), cle, ((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[+](normop `(c1[-op]c3))), (((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1))[+]((normop ` c2)[×](normop `(c1[-op]c3)))), ~H ≠ 0H)
  eqbrtrri((normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))), cle, (((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1))[+]((normop ` c2)[×](normop `(c1[-op]c3)))), (normop `(((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))[+op]((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))))
  fveq2i(cnop, (((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))[+op]((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))), ((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))
  honpncani((c0 ∘ c1), (c2 ∘ c1), (c2 ∘ c3))
  hocofi(c0, c1)
  hocofi(c2, c1)
  hocofi(c2, c3)
  mp2an((normop `(((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))[+op]((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))))[≤](((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1))[+]((normop ` c2)[×](normop `(c1[-op]c3)))), (normop `(((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))[+op]((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))))[≤]((normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1)))[+](normop `((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))), ((normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1)))[+](normop `((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))))[≤](((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1))[+]((normop ` c2)[×](normop `(c1[-op]c3)))))
  nmoptrii(((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1)), ((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))
  mp2an(((normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1)))[+](normop `((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))))[≤](((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1))[+]((normop ` c2)[×](normop `(c1[-op]c3)))), (normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1)))[≤]((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1)), (normop `((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))[≤]((normop ` c2)[×](normop `(c1[-op]c3))))
  eqbrtrri((normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))), cle, ((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1)), (normop `((c0[-op]c2)∘ c1)))
  fveq2i(cnop, ((c0[-op]c2)∘ c1), ((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1)))
  hocsubdiri(c0, c2, c1)
  ax-mp((c0 : ~H → ~H), c0 ∈ BndLinOp)
  bdopf(c0)
  ax-mp((c2 : ~H → ~H), c2 ∈ BndLinOp)
  bdopf(c2)
  nmopcoi((c0[-op]c2), c1)
  eqbrtrri((normop `((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))), cle, ((normop ` c2)[×](normop `(c1[-op]c3))), (normop `(c2 ∘(c1[-op]c3))))
  fveq2i(cnop, (c2 ∘(c1[-op]c3)), ((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))
  hoddii(c2, c1, c3)
  ax-mp(c2 ∈ LinOp, c2 ∈ BndLinOp)
  bdopln(c2)
  ax-mp((c1 : ~H → ~H), c1 ∈ BndLinOp)
  bdopf(c1)
  ax-mp((c3 : ~H → ~H), c3 ∈ BndLinOp)
  bdopf(c3)
  nmopcoi(c2, (c1[-op]c3))
  le2addi((normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))), ((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1)), (normop `((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))), ((normop ` c2)[×](normop `(c1[-op]c3))))
  letri((normop `(((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))[+op]((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))), ((normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1)))[+](normop `((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))), (((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1))[+]((normop ` c2)[×](normop `(c1[-op]c3)))))
  ax-mp((normop `(((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))[+op]((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))))∈ ℝ, (((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))[+op]((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))∈ BndLinOp)
  bdophsi(((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1)), ((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))
  nmopre((((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))[+op]((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))))
  readdcli((normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))), (normop `((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))))
  ax-mp((normop `((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1)))∈ ℝ, ((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1))∈ BndLinOp)
  bdophdi((c0 ∘ c1), (c2 ∘ c1))
  bdopcoi(c0, c1)
  nmopre(((c0 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c1)))
  ax-mp((normop `((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))∈ ℝ, ((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3))∈ BndLinOp)
  bdophdi((c2 ∘ c1), (c2 ∘ c3))
  bdopcoi(c2, c1)
  bdopcoi(c2, c3)
  nmopre(((c2 ∘ c1)[-op](c2 ∘ c3)))
  readdcli(((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1)), ((normop ` c2)[×](normop `(c1[-op]c3))))
  remulcli((normop `(c0[-op]c2)), (normop ` c1))
  ax-mp((normop ` c1)∈ ℝ, c1 ∈ BndLinOp)
  nmopre(c1)
  remulcli((normop ` c2), (normop `(c1[-op]c3)))
  ax-mp((normop ` c2)∈ ℝ, c2 ∈ BndLinOp)
  nmopre(c2)
  oveq12d(((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1)), caddc, ((normop ` c2)[×](normop `(c1[-op]c3))), (normop `(c0[-op]c2)), (normop `(c1[-op]c3)), ~H ≠ 0H)
  syl6eq(((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×](normop ` c1)), (normop `(c0[-op]c2)), ((normop `(c0[-op]c2))[×]1), ~H ≠ 0H)
  oveq2d((normop `(c0[-op]c2)), cmul, (normop ` c1), nat1, ~H ≠ 0H)
  mpan2(~H ≠ 0H, (normop ` c1)= 1, c1 ∈ UniOp)
  nmopun(c1)
  mulid1i((normop `(c0[-op]c2)))
  recni((normop `(c0[-op]c2)))
  ax-mp((normop `(c0[-op]c2))∈ ℝ, (c0[-op]c2)∈ BndLinOp)
  bdophdi(c0, c2)
  ax-mp(c0 ∈ BndLinOp, c0 ∈ UniOp)
  unopbd(c0)
  ax-mp(c2 ∈ BndLinOp, c2 ∈ UniOp)
